00:21:05.056 --> 00:21:07.142 position:50% align:center
[AOYAMA]
Aren't surprises the best?

00:21:07.225 --> 00:21:10.020 position:50% align:center
Honestly, I think they make
me happier than anything!

00:21:10.103 --> 00:21:12.647 position:50% align:center
That's why I left the message,
to raise your spirits!

00:21:12.731 --> 00:21:15.150 position:50% align:center
Did it work? Was the
cheese delicious?

00:21:15.233 --> 00:21:18.528 position:50% align:center
[IZUKU] I didn't exactly wanna
eat it off the ground!

00:21:18.611 --> 00:21:21.364 position:50% align:center
[AOYAMA] If we can't overcome
the things that bring us pain,

00:21:21.448 --> 00:21:24.951 position:50% align:center
then you won't be able
to twinkle, <i>mon ami</i> !

00:21:25.035 --> 00:21:26.995 position:50% align:center
[IZUKU]
I thought he was being creepy,

00:21:27.078 --> 00:21:30.623 position:50% align:center
but he just wanted
to encourage me.

00:21:30.707 --> 00:21:32.000 position:50% align:center
Know what, you're right.

00:21:32.083 --> 00:21:34.002 position:50% align:center
And your surprise
was a huge success.

00:21:34.085 --> 00:21:35.670 position:50% align:center
Thanks, Aoyama!

00:21:38.131 --> 00:21:40.383 position:50% align:center
Um, are you okay?

00:21:40.467 --> 00:21:42.302 position:50% align:center
[squeaking]

00:21:42.385 --> 00:21:44.095 position:50% align:center
[AOYAMA]
It came out.

00:21:47.098 --> 00:21:48.683 position:50% align:center
[IZUKU]
And so...

00:21:48.767 --> 00:21:49.934 position:50% align:center
[AOYAMA]
Try this pastry!

00:21:50.018 --> 00:21:51.227 position:50% align:center
Yeah, sure!

00:21:51.311 --> 00:21:54.898 position:50% align:center
Twinkles, you've been,
like, so cheerful lately.

00:21:54.981 --> 00:21:55.982 position:50% align:center
[IZUKU]
That's the story of how

00:21:56.066 --> 00:21:58.526 position:50% align:center
Aoyama and I became friends.

00:23:29.200 --> 00:23:30.702 position:50% align:center
[IZUKU]
Here's the preview!

00:23:30.785 --> 00:23:33.872 position:50% align:center
Autumn! It's the season
of school festivals.

00:23:33.955 --> 00:23:35.957 position:50% align:center
Those of us in the
hero course's Class 1-A

00:23:36.041 --> 00:23:37.709 position:50% align:center
were attacked by the
League of Villains

00:23:37.792 --> 00:23:40.045 position:50% align:center
and caused trouble for
the other UA students.

00:23:40.128 --> 00:23:41.588 position:50% align:center
So, to make it up to them,

00:23:41.671 --> 00:23:43.840 position:50% align:center
we're planning to put on
a special performance.

00:23:43.923 --> 00:23:45.717 position:50% align:center
We want everyone to have fun,

00:23:45.800 --> 00:23:49.637 position:50% align:center
and I want to see one little
girl smile, especially.

00:23:49.721 --> 00:23:51.890 position:50% align:center
Next time: "School Festival."

00:23:51.973 --> 00:23:54.517 position:50% align:center
I just hope no villains
ruin our plans.

